author: DAVE BYRNE | Sports Writer
title: UPDATED Girls soccer: Manheim Township, E-town and Elco earn top seeds in L-L Soccer playoffs
text:
Here are the quarterfinal pairings, sites and times for the L-L League soccer playoffs which begin Saturday. 
Elizabethtown (2-1) v. Donegal (3-2), at Penn Manor, 10:30 a.m. 
Manheim Township (1-1) v. Annville-Cleona (3-3), at Penn Manor, 12:30 p.m. 
Elco (3-1) v. Hempfield (1-3), at Manheim Central 10:30 a.m. 
Conestoga Valley (1-2) v. Cocalico (2-2), at Manheim Central, 12:30 p.m. More Headlines
